title: Bug 132103 - No objects under Context in palette when scripting a data set
OB: When scripting a data set, there are no objects displayed under the Context section in the palette.
EB: I would expect to see a list of objects under the Context section in the palette when scripting a data set.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Open the software and navigate to the data set scripting functionality.
2. Select a data set to script.
3. Look for the Context section in the palette.
4. Observe that there are no objects listed under the Context section.
